Company Overview of Mellon Optima L/S Strategy Fund, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Mellon Optima L/S Strategy Fund, LLC is a hedge fund of hedge fund launched and managed by Mellon Hedge Advisors LLC. The fund invests in funds which invest in the public equity markets of the United States. It employs long/short strategy to make its investments.  Mellon Optima L/S Strategy Fund, LLC was formed on December 14, 2004 and is domiciled in the United States.


Bny Mellon Center201 Washington StreetBoston, MA 02108-4407United StatesFounded in 2004



Phone: 617-722-7018








